social_posts.post_text: Wanna get married and get In N Out? 🍔💍
I bet not even all the fireworks in the world can light up my world like you do ❤️
Happy Birthday to the love of my life 💛
Je voudrais une martini Belvedere extra sec avec une zeste de citron s’il vous plait 🍸

A year ago today I married my best friend. It seems like I blinked and a year went by. This has been one of the most amazing and toughest years of my life. This year challenged for better, for worse and in sickness and in health.. right after our wedding I got diagnosed with a rare auto immune disease that flipped my life upside down. Jacob, you have been my rock, my number one support system, you’ve loved me and cared for me even on my toughest days. I don’t know what I would do without you. I am forever grateful to you . Thank you for always loving me, challenging me, and always pushing me to be the best version of myself. I love you forever ❤️
Make sure you Tune into the 91st annual Hollywood Christmas Parade tonight at 8pm/ 7c on @thecw 🎄🎅🏻❤️
